jffs2 - Journalling Flash File System version 2

Usage Notes
-----------

This directory include all the jffs2 vfs-adapting files.

You should call "vfs_jffs2_register" function to mount the cramfs before you can use it.

The mount point of the jffs2 in Alios-Things is "/jffs2".


Building Notes
--------------

If you want to build jffs2 in Alios-Things, you should follow these four steps:

    1. Get the Alios-Things porting version jffs2 codes first.
    you can contact us via https://github.com/alibaba/AliOS

    2. Put the souce files under this directory

    3. Add component dependency to your target board or your target app.
    e.g. $(NAME)_COMPONENTS += 3rdparty.experimental.fs.jffs2

    4. Just build and enjoy it !

